## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="78afc-102">Die folgende Tabelle zeigt die derzeit unterstützten Optionen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78afc-102">The following table shows the currently supported options.</span></span>  
  
|<span data-ttu-id="78afc-103">Kategorie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78afc-103">Category</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="78afc-104">Einstellung</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78afc-104">Setting</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="78afc-105">Wert/Wirkung</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78afc-105">Value/effect</span></span>|  
|--------------|-------------|-------------------|  
|<span data-ttu-id="78afc-106">Vertrag (Contract)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78afc-106">contract</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="78afc-107">Vererbung</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78afc-107">inheritance</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="78afc-108">`true` um die Vererbung von Datenverträgen aktivieren. `false` zu deaktivieren.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78afc-108">`true` to turn contract inheritance on; `false` to turn it off.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="78afc-109">Der Standardwert ist `true`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78afc-109">The default is `true`.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="78afc-110">Laufzeit</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78afc-110">runtime</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="78afc-111">Überprüfen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78afc-111">checking</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="78afc-112">`true` So aktivieren auf die laufzeitüberprüfung; `false` zu deaktivieren.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78afc-112">`true` to turn run-time checking on; `false` to turn it off.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="78afc-113">Der Standardwert ist `true`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78afc-113">The default is `true`.</span></span>|  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="78afc-114">Sie können dieses Attribut verwenden, wie in den folgenden Beispielen dargestellt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78afc-114">You can use this attribute as illustrated in the following examples.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="78afc-115">So deaktivieren zur Laufzeit für die gesamte Assembly überprüfen:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78afc-115">To turn off run-time checking for the entire assembly:</span></span>  
  
```  
[assembly:ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="78afc-116">Zum Überprüfen der Laufzeit-Vertrag für einen bestimmten Typ aktivieren:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78afc-116">To turn run-time contract checking on for a specific type:</span></span>  
  
```  
   [ContractOption("runtime", "checking", true)]  
   class TypeWithRuntimeChecking {  
  
       ...  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="78afc-117">Für eine bestimmte Methode deaktivieren laufzeitüberprüfung:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78afc-117">To turn run-time checking off for a specific method:</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Turn off all contract inheritance from interface IList<T>  
[ContractOption("contract", "inheritance", false)]  
class MyConcurrentList<T> : IList<T> {  
   ...  
}  
  
[ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
public override MyMethod(int x) {  
   // no inherited contracts checked at runtime,  
   // no invariants checked at runtime.  
   ...  
}  
  
       [ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
       public void MethodWithoutRuntimeChecking(...) {  
          ...  
       }  
   }  
  
```
